main event: A sergeant from Springfield, Ohio reported finding two pieces of aluminum material on her farm in 1964.
interesting points: The pieces of metal measured approximately 4 inches by 5 inches,The metal was painted green and yellow,The witness contacted the Air Force to get an opinion on the material,The call was made to Wright-Patterson Air Force Base for investigation,The report is part of Project Blue Book UFO investigations.
sighted object: two pieces of aluminum painted green and yellow
